- "Maintaining strong overall performance" means the total store sales from the performance table are more than 75% of the actual sales;
- "Sufficient workforce" means the average number of employees is greater than 5.

- "Top three product families" refers to the product families with the highest total sales for each store;
- "Stars of the sales show" metaphorically represents the most successful or prominent product families;
